      "description": "$5,900 - Poor-condition car. It runs, but it has significant wear and problems consistent with a vehicle in rough shape. Expect noticeable cosmetic damage, interior wear, deferred maintenance, and repairs needed to keep it on the road. Best suited for someone looking for a project, parts, or basic transportation with work involved.",
