    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition example that presents nicely overall and should make a solid driver for its next owner. The body, paint, and trim show well, with the normal age-related cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect on a car of this vintage, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. The interior is tidy and usable, showing some signs of age and regular use rather than neglect. Overall, this is an honest, presentable car for someone looking for a good driver-quality example rather than a show car.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "Runs and drives, but this is a poor-condition vehicle best suited for someone looking for cheap transportation, a project, or possibly a parts car. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with visible age, blemishes, and a tired overall presentation. Expect a worn interior, deferred maintenance, and the likelihood that it will need repairs and attention to be dependable. This is an inexpensive, as-is vehicle for a buyer who understands what a rough used car is and is not expecting a clean or fully sorted example.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Project-grade car in poor overall condition and best suited for a buyer who wants a restoration candidate, a heavy fixer-upper, or a parts source. It shows clear age, cosmetic wear, and neglect throughout, with tired paint, visible exterior flaws, worn trim, aged glass, and an interior that should be expected to need substantial cleaning and refurbishment. This is not a turnkey driver, and buyers should assume deferred maintenance, possible mechanical issues, and the likelihood of repairs before it can be used regularly. Please come with realistic expectations and plan on a thorough inspection; it\u2019s an honest rough example being sold as-is.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Solid, honest driver with plenty of character and a nice opportunity for someone who wants an enjoyable car at a sensible price. This one shows visible age and wear consistent with a fair-condition example, so it\u2019s not a showpiece, but it presents decently, feels complete, and should appeal to a buyer who values usability over perfection. A good candidate for weekend cruising, casual enjoyment, or gradual improvement while driving and appreciating it.",
      "price": 17900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
